##DNS: Domain name system

1. Converet user friendly names to their associated IP (forward)

2. Convert a known IP address to its associated user friendly name (reverse)

DNS can update IP addresses automatically and dynamically

Flat namespace: peer to peer (hosts are equal to eachother) These have size limitations: hostfiles use these

Most systems are heirarchical

first computer in a system must be a server
	-Primary domain controller (PDC): Now called Domain controller
	#Start of Authority (SOA): 



**WINS: windows internet naming system (deprecated)


